<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Users Data Export</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3554D1;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3554D1;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .info {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3554D1;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Users Data Export</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello Administrator,</p>
            
            <p>As requested, attached is the CSV export of all users from your system.</p>
            
            <div class="info">
                <p><strong>Export Details:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Total Users: {{ userCount }}</li>
                    <li>Export Date: {{ exportDate }}</li>
                    <li>File Format: CSV</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>The CSV file includes: user ID, name, email, role, phone number, gender, and account status.</p>
            
            <p>For security reasons, this data has been sent to your administrator email instead of being downloaded directly.</p>
            
            <p>If you did not request this export, please contact your system administrator immediately.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you,<br>Go Trip Admin System</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Go Trip. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
